{"kanda":6,"sarga":102,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"शक्त्याविनिहतंदृष्टवारावणेनबलीयसा ।लक्ष्मणंसमरेशूरंरूधिरौघपरिप्लुतम् स दत्त्वातुमुलंयुद्धंरावणस्यदुरात्मनः ।विसृजन्नेवबाणौघान् सुषेणमिदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Seeing Lakshmana struck by exceedingly mighty, evil minded Ravana's javelin and soaked in blood Rama giving intense fight by discharging arrows also spoke as follows to Sushena.","words":[{"d":"बलीयसा","m":"exceedingly mighty"},{"d":"रावणेन","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"शक्त्या","m":"by the javelin"},{"d":"विनिहतम्","m":"struck"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in fight"},{"d":"शूरम्","m":"heroic"},{"d":"रूधिरौघपरिप्लुतम्","m":"soaked in blood"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"तुमुलम्","m":"intense"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"fight"},{"d":"दत्त्वा","m":"given"},{"d":"बाणौघान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विसृजन्नेव","m":"even discharging"},{"d":"सुषेणम्","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"शक्त्याविनिहतंदृष्टवारावणेनबलीयसा ।लक्ष्मणंसमरेशूरंरूधिरौघपरिप्लुतम् स दत्त्वातुमुलंयुद्धंरावणस्यदुरात्मनः ।विसृजन्नेवबाणौघान् सुषेणमिदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Seeing Lakshmana struck by exceedingly mighty, evil minded Ravana's javelin and soaked in blood Rama giving intense fight by discharging arrows also spoke as follows to Sushena.","words":[{"d":"बलीयसा","m":"exceedingly mighty"},{"d":"रावणेन","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"शक्त्या","m":"by the javelin"},{"d":"विनिहतम्","m":"struck"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in fight"},{"d":"शूरम्","m":"heroic"},{"d":"रूधिरौघपरिप्लुतम्","m":"soaked in blood"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"तुमुलम्","m":"intense"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"fight"},{"d":"दत्त्वा","m":"given"},{"d":"बाणौघान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विसृजन्नेव","m":"even discharging"},{"d":"सुषेणम्","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"एषरावणवीर्येणलक्ष्मणःपतितोभुविः ।सर्पवच्चेष्टतेवीरोभूमौशोकमुदिरीयन्","trans":"'Heroic Lakshmana struck by Ravana, fell on the ground and writhing like a snake and rolling made me sad'.","words":[{"d":"रावणवीर्येण","m":"prowess of Ravana"},{"d":"भुवि","m":"earth"},{"d":"पतितः","m":"fallen"},{"d":"एषः","m":"like that"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणः","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"शोकम्","m":"sorrow"},{"d":"उदीरयन्","m":"writhing"},{"d":"सर्पवत्","m":"like snake"},{"d":"भूमौ","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"चेष्टते","m":"rolling"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"शोणितार्द्रमिमंवीरंप्राणैःप्रियतरंमम ।पश्यतोममकाशक्तिर्योद्धुंपर्याकुलात्मनः","trans":"' As I see Lakshmana, who is more than my life, and loving soaked in blood, my mind is agitated. How can I have the energy to fight?'","words":[{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"प्राणैः","m":"more than life"},{"d":"प्रियतरम्","m":"loving"},{"d":"शोणितार्द्रम्","m":"soaked in blood"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"this way"},{"d":"वीरम्","m":"heroic"},{"d":"पश्यतः","m":"as I see"},{"d":"पर्याकुलात्मनः","m":"mind agitated"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"योद्धुम्","m":"to fight"},{"d":"शक्तिः","m":"energy"},{"d":"का","m":"how"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"अ यं स समरश्लाघीभ्रातामेशुभलक्षणः ।यदिपञ्चत्वमापन्नःप्राणैर्मेकिंसुखेनवा","trans":"'Lakshmana, my brother, is praised for his efficiency in war, is endowed with auspicious marks. If he is met with death, what use is my happiness and life for me?'","words":[{"d":"समरश्लाघी","m":"praised for efficiency in war"},{"d":"शुभलक्षणः","m":"endowed with auspicious marks"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"पञ्चत्वम्","m":"death"},{"d":"आपन्नःयदि","m":"if meets"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"प्राणैः","m":"life"},{"d":"सुखेनवा","m":"happiness"},{"d":"किम्","m":"What use"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"लज्जतीवहिवीर्यंभ्रश्यतीवकराद्धनुः ।सायकाव्यवसीदन्तिदृष्टिर्भाष्पवशंगता","trans":"'My heroism is shy, my bow slips from my hand, arrows are dropping, my vision is blurred with tears with my brother gone.'","words":[{"d":"वीर्यम्","m":"heroism"},{"d":"लज्जतीव","m":"shy"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"करात्","m":"from hand"},{"d":"भ्रश्यतीव","m":"slip from"},{"d":"सायकाः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"व्यवसीदन्ति","m":"dropping"},{"d":"दृष्टिः","m":"vision"},{"d":"बाष्पवशम्","m":"filled with tears"},{"d":"गताहि","m":"gone"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"अवसीदन्तिगात्राणिस्वप्नयानेनृणामिव ।चिन्तामेवर्ततेतीव्रामुमूर्षापि च जायते","trans":"'Seeing Lakshmana in this state, just as in dream, my limbs are retrieving while walking, being on the point of death intense sorrow is growing and the desire to live is gone.'","words":[{"d":"स्वप्नयाने","m":"in dream"},{"d":"नृणामिव","m":"while walking"},{"d":"गात्राणि","m":"limbs"},{"d":"अवसीदन्ति","m":"retrieves"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"चिन्ता","m":"grief"},{"d":"तीव्रा","m":"intense"},{"d":"वर्तते","m":"growing"},{"d":"मुमूर्षापि च","m":"being on the point of death"},{"d":"जायते","m":"desire to live is going"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"भ्रातरंनिहतंदृष्टवारावणेनदुरात्मना ।विष्टनन्तंतुदुःखार्तंमर्मण्यभिहतंभृशम्","trans":"Seeing the brother struck in vital parts and wounded by the evilminded Ravana, Rama was filled with grief and breathing heavily.","words":[{"d":"दुरात्मना","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"रावणेन","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"wounded"},{"d":"विष्टनन्तम्","m":"filled with grief"},{"d":"दुःखार्तम्","m":"sad"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"breathing heavily"},{"d":"मर्मणि","m":"vital parts"},{"d":"अभिहतम्","m":"struck"},{"d":"भ्रातरम्","m":"brother"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"राघवोभ्रातरंदृष्टवाप्रियंप्राणंबहिश्चरम् ।दुःखेनमहताविष्टोध्यानशोकपरायणः","trans":"Beholding his dear brother, who is his life outside him overcome by anxiety, Rama lost senses and gave himself to great sorrow.","words":[{"d":"राघवो","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"भ्रातरं","m":"brother"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"प्रियं","m":"dear"},{"d":"प्राणंबहिश्चरम्","m":"life outside"},{"d":"दुःखेन","m":"in grief"},{"d":"महताविष्टो","m":"overcome by anxiety"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"परंविषादमापन्नोविललापाकुलेन्द्रियः ।भ्रातरंनिहतंदृष्टवालक्ष्मणंरणपांसुषु","trans":"Seeing the wounded brother Lakshmana in the battlefield, the very sad Rama lost control over his senses and grieved.","words":[{"d":"निहतम्","m":"wounded"},{"d":"भ्रातरम्","m":"brother"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"रणपांसुषु","m":"in the battlefield"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"परम्","m":"very"},{"d":"विषादम्","m":"sad"},{"d":"आपन्नः","m":"overtaken"},{"d":"विललाप","m":"grieved"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"विजयोऽपिहिमेशूर न प्रियायोपकल्पते ।अचक्षुर्विषयश्चन्द्रःकांप्रीतिंजनयिष्यति","trans":"'O Hero! Even victory for me will not give joy. What pleasure will one have if he desires to see the moon when he has lost vision?'","words":[{"d":"शूर","m":"hero"},{"d":"विजयोपि","m":"if victorious"},{"d":"मे","m":"for me"},{"d":"प्रियाय","m":"loving"},{"d":"न उपकल्पते","m":"not give joy"},{"d":"अचक्षुर्विषयः","m":"for one who has lost vision"},{"d":"चन्द्रः","m":"moon"},{"d":"काम्","m":"desire"},{"d":"प्रीतिम् जनयिष्यति","m":"What pleasure will it give"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"किंमेयुद्धेनकिंप्राणैर्युद्धकार्यं न विद्यते ।यत्रायंनिहतश्शेतेरणमूर्धनिलक्ष्मणः","trans":"'What purpose is there to fight in battle or in life with Lakshmana lying in the forefront struck in the battlefield?'","words":[{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"युद्धेन","m":"in the battle"},{"d":"किम्","m":"what"},{"d":"प्राणैः","m":"life"},{"d":"किम्","m":"what"},{"d":"अयंलक्ष्मणः","m":"this Lakshmana"},{"d":"रणमूर्धनि","m":"in the forefront of battle"},{"d":"निहतः","m":"struck"},{"d":"यत्र","m":"here"},{"d":"शेते","m":"lying"},{"d":"युद्धकार्यम्","m":"purpose of fighting"},{"d":"न विद्यते","m":"not known"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"यथैवमांवनंयान्तमनुयातिमहाद्युतिः ।अहमप्युपयास्यामितथैवैनंयमक्षयम्","trans":"'Lakshmana who is endowed with splendour followed me to the forest. In the same way I will follow him to the god of death.'","words":[{"d":"महाद्युतिः","m":"endowed with splendour"},{"d":"वनम्","m":"forest"},{"d":"यान्तम्","m":"followed"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"यथैव","m":"in the same way"},{"d":"अनुयाति","m":"follow"},{"d":"अहमपि","m":"I also"},{"d":"तथैव","m":"in the same way"},{"d":"यमक्षयम्","m":"god of death"},{"d":"उपयास्यामि","m":"follow him"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"इष्टबन्धुजनोनित्यंमां स नित्यमनुव्रतः ।इमामवस्थांगमितोराक्षसैःकूटयोधिभिः","trans":"'Lakshmana, who loved the kin and was devoted to me, has been led to pass by the Rakshasas.'","words":[{"d":"इष्टबन्धुजनः","m":"loved kin"},{"d":"नित्यम्","m":"always"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"अनुव्रतः","m":"devoted to me"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"कूटयोधिभिः","m":"has been led to"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"इमाम्","m":"this way"},{"d":"अवस्थाम्","m":"situation"},{"d":"गमितः","m":"pass by"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"देशेदेशेकलत्राणिदेशेदेशे च बान्दवाः ।तंतुदेशं न पश्यामियत्रभ्रातासहोदरः","trans":"'Wives can be found everywhere, relatives can be found everywhere but biological sibling brothers are not found in any place.'","words":[{"d":"देशेदेशे","m":"everywhere"},{"d":"कलत्राणि","m":"wives"},{"d":"देशेदेशे च","m":"everywhere"},{"d":"बान्दवाः","m":"relatives"},{"d":"सहोदरः","m":"sibling brother"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"यत्र","m":"here"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"देशंतु","m":"no place"},{"d":"न पश्यामि","m":"not found"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"इत्येवंविलपन्तंतंशोकविह्वलितेद्रनियम् ।विवेष्टमानंकरुणमच्छवसन्तंपुनःपुनः राममाश्वासयनवीरसुषेनोवाक्यमब्रवीत","trans":"Grieving in this manner, lost control over senses, and discrimination, Rama was sighing again and again and was pitiable. Sushena, the hero consoling Rama spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"इत्येवम्","m":"in this manner"},{"d":"विलपन्तम्","m":"grieving"},{"d":"शोकविह्वलितेद्रनियम्","m":"lost control over senses in grief विवेष्टमानम् lost sense of discrimination"},{"d":"पुनःपुनः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"करुणम्","m":"pitiable"},{"d":"उच्छवसन्तम्","m":"sighing"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"सुषेनो","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"आस्वसयन","m":"consoling"},{"d":"अब्रवीत","m":"spoke"},{"d":"वाक्यम","m":"words"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"किनुराज्येनदुर्धर्षलक्ष्मणेनविनामम ।कथंवक्ष्याम्यहंत्वम्बांसुमित्रांपुत्रवत्सलाम्","trans":"'Without Lakshmana who is difficult to win, what use is kingdom to me? What can I tell mother Sumithra who is the lover of her son?'","words":[{"d":"दुर्धर्षलक्ष्मणेनविना","m":"without Lakshmana who is difficult to win"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"राज्येन","m":"kingdom"},{"d":"किंनु","m":"why"},{"d":"पुत्रवत्सलाम्","m":"lover of son"},{"d":"अम्बाम्","m":"mother"},{"d":"सुमित्राम्","m":"to Sumithra"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"किंनुवक्ष्यामि","m":"What can I tell"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"न मृथोयंमहाबाहो लक्ष्मणोलक्षमिवर्धन: ।न चास्यविक्रतंवक्त्रानापिशस्वासं न निष्प्रभं","trans":"O Broad shouldered Rama! Enhancer of prosperity, Lakshmana is not dead. His face has not changed, and he has not lost splendour.","words":[{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"O broad shouldered"},{"d":"लक्षमिवर्धन:","m":"enhancer of prosperity"},{"d":"न मृथो","m":"not dead"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"सुप्रभंसुप्रसन्नं च मुखमस्यनिरीक्ष्यताम् पद्मपत्रतलौहस्तौसुप्रसन्ने च लोचने ।","trans":"'His face is radiant and pleasing to see. His palms are like red lotuses and his eyes are so pleasant'.","words":[{"d":"सुप्रभम्","m":"radiant"},{"d":"सुप्रसन्नं","m":"pleasing"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"मुखम्","m":"face"},{"d":"निरीक्ष्यताम्","m":"seeing"},{"d":"हस्तौ","m":"palms"},{"d":"पद्मपत्रतलौ","m":"red lotus like"},{"d":"लोचने च","m":"and eyes"},{"d":"सुप्रसन्ने","m":"very pleasant"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"ऐ वं न विद्यतेरूपंगतासूनांविशम्पते माविषादंमृकृथावीरसप्राणोऽयमरिन्दम ।","trans":"\"O hero! Those who cease to live will not have such appearance and signs. He who is a tamer of foes is alive. I tell you, do not grieve.\"","words":[{"d":"विशम्पते","m":"such form"},{"d":"वीर","m":"heroes"},{"d":"गतासूनाम्","m":"ceased of life"},{"d":"रूपम्","m":"form"},{"d":"ईदृशब्","m":"marks"},{"d":"न दृश्यते","m":"not seen"},{"d":"अरिन्दम","m":"tamer of foes"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"सप्राणः","m":"those who are alive"},{"d":"विषादम्","m":"grief"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"आ ख्यासतितुप्रसुप्तस्यस्रस्तगात्रस्यभूतले सोच्छवासंहृदयंवीरकम्पमानंमुहुर्मुहुः ।","trans":"\"From the movement of his limbs and throbbing of his heart again and again it is known that he is alive.\"","words":[{"d":"तु","m":"you"},{"d":"प्रसुप्तस्य","m":"fallen thus"},{"d":"स्रस्तगात्रस्य","m":"from the limbs"},{"d":"सोच्छवासम्","m":"lying alive"},{"d":"मुहुर्मुहुः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"कम्पमानम्","m":"throbbing"},{"d":"हृदयम्","m":"heart"},{"d":"आख्याति","m":"is known"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वामहाप्राज्ञःसुषेणोराघवंवचः समीपस्थमुवाचेदंहनूमन्तंमहाकपिम् ।","trans":"Very wise Sushena, having spoken like that to Raghava, spoke to the great Vanara, Hanuman nearby.","words":[{"d":"महाप्राज्ञः","m":"very wise"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"समीपस्थम्","m":"nearby"},{"d":"महाकपिम्","m":"great Vanara"},{"d":"हनूमन्तम्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"सौम्य शीघ्रमितोगत्वाशैलमौषधिपर्वतम् पूर्वंतुकथितोयोऽसौवीर जाम्बवताशुभ: ।दक्षिणेशिखरेजातामोषधिमानय सवर्णकरणींनाम्नासावर्ण्यकरणींतथा ।सञ्जीवकरणींवीरसन्धानीं च महौषधीम् सञ्जीवनार्धंवीरस्यलक्ष्मणस्यमहात्मनः ।","trans":"\"O gentle Hanumantha! Going to that mountain of herbs about which Jambavan had earlier spoken to you, get the herbs from the southern peak of that great mountain. To make Lakshmana the great soul alive quickly go and get Savarankarani, Sarvakarani so also Sanjeevakarani and Sandhanakarani and come.\"","words":[{"d":"सौम्य","m":"gentle"},{"d":"वीर","m":"heroic"},{"d":"यःअसौ","m":"that which"},{"d":"पूर्वम्","m":"earlier"},{"d":"जाम्बवता","m":"Jambavantha"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"कथितः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"औषथिपर्वतम्","m":"mountain of herbs"},{"d":"शैलम्","m":"peak"},{"d":"इतः","m":"now"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"दक्षिणेशिखरे","m":"southern peak"},{"d":"जाताम्","m":"having gone"},{"d":"नाम्ना","m":"by name"},{"d":"सवर्णकरणीम्","m":"Sarvakarani"},{"d":"महौषधिम्","m":"great herb"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"सावर्ण्यकरणीम