 high speed"},{"d":"हनुमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"समागम्य","m":"came"},{"d":"गिरेः","m":"mountain"},{"d":"किञ्चित्","m":"for a while"},{"d":"विश्रम्","m":"resting"},{"d":"सुषेणम्","m":"to Sushena"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":34,"dev":"ओषधीर्नावगच्छामिताअहंहरिपुङ्गव तदिदंशिखरंकृत्स्नंगिरेस्तस्याहृतंमया ।","trans":"\"O leader of the Vanaras! I did not know those herbs. So, the mountain peak was brought here by me.\"","words":[{"d":"हरिपुङ्गव","m":"leader of Vanaras"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"ताः","m":"those"},{"d":"नावगच्छामि","m":"did not know"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"here"},{"d":"कृत्स्नम्","m":"dark"},{"d":"शिखरम्","m":"peak"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"आहृतम्","m":"brought"}]},{"v":35,"dev":"एवंकथयमानंतुप्रशस्यपवनात्मजम् सुषेणोवानरश्रेष्ठोजग्राहोत्पाट्यचौषधीः ।","trans":"The son of wind god, having revealed it like that, Sushena the leader of the Vanaras uprooted the herb and took out.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"कथयमानम्","m":"having revealed"},{"d":"पवनात्मजम्","m":"by the son of wind god"},{"d":"प्रशस्य","m":"applauding"},{"d":"वानरश्रेष्ठः","m":"leader of the Vanaras"},{"d":"सुषेणः","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"ओषधीः","m":"herb"},{"d":"उत्पाट्य","m":"uprooted"},{"d":"जग्राह","m":"took up"}]},{"v":36,"dev":"विस्मितास्तुबभूवुस्तेसर्वेवानरपुङ्गवाः दृष्टवाहनूमतःकर्मसुरैरपिसुदुष्करम् ।","trans":"It is a difficult task even for Suras. Seeing Hanuman doing it all the Vanara leaders were amazed.","words":[{"d":"सुरैरपि","m":"even for Suras"},{"d":"सुदुष्करम्","m":"very difficult"},{"d":"हनूमतः","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"task"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"them"},{"d":"वानरपुङ्गवाः","m":"Vanara leaders"},{"d":"विस्मिताः","m":"amazed"},{"d":"बभूवुः","m":"were"}]},{"v":37,"dev":"ततःसङ्क्षोदयित्वातामोषधिंवानरोत्तमः लक्ष्मणस्यददौनस्तस्सुषेणस्सुमहाद्युतिः ।","trans":"Thereafter, Sushena the foremost of the Vanaras, a brilliant one crushed the herbs and dropped the extract into Lakshmana's nose.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"वानरोत्तमः","m":"foremost of Vanaras"},{"d":"सुमहाद्युतिः","m":"brilliant"},{"d":"सुषेणः","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"them"},{"d":"ओषधिम्","m":"herbs"},{"d":"सङ्क्षोदयित्वा","m":"crushed"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणस्य","m":"Lakshmana's"},{"d":"नस्तः","m":"nose"},{"d":"ददौ","m":"dropped"}]},{"v":38,"dev":"विशल्यस्ससमाघ्रायलक्ष्मणःपरवीरहा विशल्योविरुजश्शीघ्रमुदतिष्ठन्महीतलात् ।","trans":"The destroyer of enemies, Lakshmana, who was pained by the javelin stuck in his body, on inhaling the herb, was devoid of javelin and rid of pain. He got up from the ground.","words":[{"d":"सशल्यः","m":"pained with piercing of that javelin"},{"d":"परवीरहा","m":"destroyer of enemies"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणः","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"समाघ्राय","m":"inhaling"},{"d":"विशल्यः","m":"devoid of javelin"},{"d":"विरुजः","m":"rid of pain"},{"d":"महीतलात्","m":"from the ground"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"उदतिष्ठत्","m":"got up"}]},{"v":39,"dev":"तमुत्थितंतुहरयोभूतलात्प्रेक्ष्यलक्ष्मणम् साधुसावधितिसुप्रीतालक्ष्मणंप्रत्यपूजयन् ।","trans":"Seeing Lakshmana rise up from the surface of the ground, the Vanaras said Well done and offered prayers very affectionately.","words":[{"d":"हरयः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"भूतलात्","m":"from the surface of the ground"},{"d":"उत्थितम्","m":"arisen"},{"d":"तंलक्ष्मणम्","m":"that Lakshmana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सुप्रीताः","m":"very affectionately"},{"d":"साधुसाधुइति","m":"well done well done"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"प्रत्यपूजयन्","m":"in turn offered prayers"}]},{"v":40,"dev":"एह्येहीत्यब्रवीद्रामोलक्ष्मणंपरवीरहा सस्वजेस्नेहगाढं च बाष्पपर्याकुलेक्षणः ।","trans":"Rama the destroyer of enemies seeing Lakshmana saying, 'come come', eyes filled with tears of joy affectionately embraced him and spoke.","words":[{"d":"परवीरहा","m":"destroyer of enemies"},{"d":"एहिएहि","m":"come"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":