 truthful valour"},{"d":"पुरा","m":"earlier"},{"d":"तांप्रतिज्ञाम्","m":"you having made a vow"},{"d":"प्रतिज्ञाय","m":"vow"},{"d":"असत्त्वः","m":"weak minded"},{"d":"लघुः","m":"lowly"},{"d":"कश्चिदिव","m":"spiritless"},{"d":"इह","m":"now"},{"d":"ए वम्","m":"this way"},{"d":"वक्तुम्","m":"speaking"},{"d":"न अर्हसि","m":"not appropriate"}]},{"v":45,"dev":"न हिप्रतिज्ञांकुर्वन्तिवितथांसत्यवादिनः लक्षणंहिमहत्त्वस्यप्रतिज्ञापरिपालनम् ।","trans":"'Those who speak truth never fail their vows futile for fulfilment of the vows is a mark of greatness for them'.","words":[{"d":"सत्यवादिनः","m":"those who speak truth"},{"d":"प्रतिज्ञाम्","m":"vows"},{"d":"वितथाम्","m":"futile"},{"d":"न कुर्वन्तिहि","m":"never make"},{"d":"प्रतिज्ञापरिपालनम्","m":"for fulfilment of vow"},{"d":"महत्त्वस्य","m":"greatness"},{"d":"लक्षणंहि","m":"mark of vow"}]},{"v":46,"dev":"नैराश्यमुपगन्तुं च नालंतेमत्कृतेऽनघ वधेनरावणस्याद्यप्रतिज्ञामनुपालय ।","trans":"\"O Sinless Rama! To be in despair on my account is not fair. Destroy Ravana and redeem your vow.\"","words":[{"d":"अनघ","m":"sinless"},{"d":"मत्कृते","m":"on my account"},{"d":"नैराश्यम्","m":"to despair"},{"d":"उपगन्तुं च","m":"to give up"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"वधेन","m":"destruction"},{"d":"प्रतिज्ञाम्","m":"vow"},{"d":"अनुपालय","m":"fulfill"}]},{"v":47,"dev":"नजीवन्यास्यतेशत्रुस्तवबाणपथंगतः नर्दतस्तीक्षणदंष्ट्रस्यसिंहस्येवमहागजः ।","trans":"\" A victim of your arrow can not be alive just as an elephant fallen into the clutch of a roaring lion with sharp teeth is not possible to live.\"","words":[{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"बाणपथम्","m":"victim of your arrow"},{"d":"महागजःइव","m":"like an elephant"},{"d":"जीवन्","m":"live"},{"d":"न यास्यते","m":"not possible"}]},{"v":48,"dev":"अहंतुवधमिच्छामिशीघ्रमस्यदुरात्मनः यावदस्तं न यात्येषकृतकर्मादिवाकरः ।","trans":"\"I wish to see the destruction of this evil minded one quickly before the sun completes the day and sets.\"","words":[{"d":"दिवाकरः","m":"Sun"},{"d":"कृतकर्मा","m":"having completed his day"},{"d":"यावत्","m":"before"},{"d":"अस्तम्","m":"sets"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"वधम्","m":"destruction"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"wish"}]}]}